Available Tools: list_processes | kill_process | get_process_info | top_processes
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "pid": "number", "name": "string", "signal": "string" }
Response Schema: { "processes": [{ "pid": "number", "name": "string", "cpu": "number", "mem": "number" }] }
---
Question: Display the top 4 processes sorted by CPU utilization.
Call: { "func_call": "top_processes", "pid": null, "name": null, "signal": null }
Response: { "processes": [{ "pid": 7821, "name": "redis-server", "cpu": 38.9, "mem": 15.2 }, { "pid": 4102, "name": "code", "cpu": 29.4, "mem": 21.3 }, { "pid": 905, "name": "slack", "cpu": 18.7, "mem": 19.8 }, { "pid": 3340, "name": "zoom", "cpu": 14.2, "mem": 11.5 }] }

Question: Retrieve statistics for the process with ID 5512.
Call: { "func_call": "get_process_info", "pid": 5512, "name": null, "signal": null }
Response: { "processes": [{ "pid": 5512, "name": "mongod", "cpu": 12.3, "mem": 28.9 }] }

Question: Enumerate every active process on this machine.
Call: { "func_call": "list_processes", "pid": null, "name": null, "signal": null }
Response: { "processes": [{ "pid": 1, "name": "init", "cpu": 0.0, "mem": 0.2 }, { "pid": 302, "name": "cron", "cpu": 0.1, "mem": 0.4 }, { "pid": 7821, "name": "redis-server", "cpu": 38.9, "mem": 15.2 }, { "pid": 5512, "name": "mongod", "cpu": 12.3, "mem": 28.9 }] }

